data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Beautiful Inground Pool!!!!  New roof installed before closing or $15,000 cash back to buyer at closing for closing costs or to lower points for interest. Florida living is meant to be enjoyed outdoors with grilling and get-togethers.  This home is perfect for socializing with family and friends with your oversized screen lanai that directly overlooks the  sparkling outdoor pool (new pump and filter system). This 3 bedroom, 2 bath home has plenty of room inside, a large living room, and a family room.  The eat-in kitchen and baths have granite countertops and tile flooring. There is plenty of storage in the rich wood kitchen cabinets, walk-in closet, and inside laundry room with shelving. Your dining room with its expansive sliding glass doors leading to the lanai and master bedroom opening to the backyard gives you the feeling of being outdoors.  Within a couple of miles of the new Amazon distribution centers and the upcoming Deltona Village with restaurants and shopping. Owner Realtor
